| cust_id | first_name | last_name |
+---------+------------+-----------+
|       1 | Suraj      | surve     |
|       2 | Pravin     | sukale    |
|       3 | Mayur      | devkar    |
|       4 | Pankaj     | chatter   |
|       5 | Mahek      | jaswal    |
+---------+------------+-----------+

 Orders Table:

 mysql> select * from orders;
+----------+---------+-----------+--------------+------------+
| order_id | cust_id | product   | total_amount | order_date |
+----------+---------+-----------+--------------+------------+
|        1 |       1 | Laptop    |     49000.00 | 2025-04-05 |
|        2 |       2 | Mobile    |     30000.00 | 2025-01-03 |
|        3 |       3 | Headphone |       199.00 | 2025-04-11 |
|        4 |       4 | tab       |     40000.00 | 2025-12-03 |
|        5 |       5 | case      |        49.00 | 2025-01-05 |
+----------+---------+-----------+--------------+------------+
============================================================================================================================================================================================
Q1 .Write an SQL query to retrieve the first and last names of customers along with the
 order date and total amount of their orders. Use an INNER JOIN to connect the two
 tables.
-->
    -> select c.first_name,c.last_name,o.order_date,o.product,o.total_amount
    -> from customers c
    -> inner join orders o on c.cust_id = o.cust_id;
+------------+-----------+------------+-----------+--------------+
| first_name | last_name | order_date | product   | total_amount |
+------------+-----------+------------+-----------+--------------+
| Suraj      | surve     | 2025-04-05 | Laptop    |     49000.00 |
| Pravin     | sukale    | 2025-01-03 | Mobile    |     30000.00 |
| Mayur      | devkar    | 2025-04-11 | Headphone |       199.00 |
| Pankaj     | chatter   | 2025-12-03 | tab       |     40000.00 |
| Mahek      | jaswal    | 2025-01-05 | case      |        49.00 |
+------------+-----------+------------+-----------+--------------+

============================================================================================================================================================================================

