============================================================================================================================================================================================

Q2 . Write an SQL query to retrieve a list of all departments and the names of employees
 who belong to each department. Use a LEFT JOIN to include departments that have no
 employees
   --> select d.dept_name,e.first_name,e.last_name
    -> from department d
    -> left join employee e on d.dept_id=e.dept_id;
+-----------+------------+-----------+
| dept_name | first_name | last_name |
+-----------+------------+-----------+
| HR        | suraj      | surve     |
| HR        | poonum     | kamble    |
| IT        | parvin     | sukale    |
| IT        | mayur      | devkar    |
| Finance   | mahek      | jaswal    |
| Marketing | aunshka    | kamble    |
+-----------+------------+-----------+

